# Domain — Billing Rules

- Use **idempotency keys** for payment and subscription operations
- Never log full card or payment method details
- Validate webhook signatures (e.g. Stripe) before processing
- Store only safe identifiers (customer_id, subscription_id); no raw card data
- Handle subscription lifecycle (created, updated, canceled, past_due) explicitly
- Use environment variables for API keys; never commit

Keep billing logic in a dedicated service; do not mix with generic CRUD.

Test with provider test mode and webhook fixtures.
